Vaeli OC

Hello everyone! This is Spixy and you guys likely are here from the Unstable Diffusion Discord server. And I know quite a few of you love her and so I have made an embed for our convenience!

Also an honourable mention for my friend ROOD for providing these awesome example images! <3
